{
  "stem": "21349.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't have to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if they didn't know I was a Jew, they would beat me up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the thing is [LAUGHS] one day the teacher, just a little bit after Hitler came to power, came over to me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said to me, it was a French teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He comes from Alsace-Lorraine, which is at the border between Germany and France, near Strasbourg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to me, here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have here the emblem of the Nazi Party, which is like a ring and the swastika in the middle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it says in NASDP, NSDAP, which is the abbreviation of the Nazi, Nationalsocialistishe Deutsch Arbeiterpartei.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said to me, I had to put it on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is my life saver.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was a double ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But don't think that I really feel this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And many times in our business, former people who belong to Communist party came to us, and they talked to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they said to me, they said to my father, consider me a burnt pancake.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Do you know what a burnt pancake is?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It's brown from the outside and red from the inside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they put on a Nazi uniform, and they still were Communists, because they had burnt inside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Was your father political at all?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was not political-- he was not political in any sense.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He never wanted to be political.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, he told me that in 1929, when they had the inflation, the Germans wanted to send-- wanted to sell German citizenship for 50 marks, very cheap.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came again and again, and said, why don't you buy it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father said, I don't want to buy any kind of political-- any kind of political things.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
